svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Juli 31, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104qom1665703129290.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/qom1665703129290.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/qom1665703129290.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"qom1665703129290\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      Script Container\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body refbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Location for defining the ProcScript modules of the associated object.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"qom1665703129290__section_w2569ab1b5b3_w2570ab1b5_w2571ab1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1215551e51\"> Description </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"qom1665703129290__p_d115886e1_d115887e1_d115888e1\">The Script code container can contain:</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"qom1665703129290__li_d44201e1_d44202e1_d44203e1\">Constant declarations with container scope </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"qom1665703129290__li_d44204e1_d44205e1_d44206e1\">System triggers </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"qom1665703129290__li_d44207e1_d44208e1_d44209e1\">Interactive triggers </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"qom1665703129290__li_d44210e1_d44211e1_d44212e1\">Operations </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"qom1665703129290__li_d44213e1_d44214e1_d44215e1\">Web triggers and operations (in DSP components) </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"qom1665703129290__li_d44216e1_d44217e1_d44218e1\">Functions </li>\n<li class=\"li\">Entries</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"note note note_note\" id=\"qom1665703129290__note_w2572ab1b5b3b7_w2573ab1b5b3_w2574ab1b5_w2575ab1\"><span class=\"note__title\">Note:</span> Entities have two\n        Script containers—Collection Script and Occurrence Script for defining entity-level\n        (collection) and occurrence-level processing.</div>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"qom1665703129290__p_d115889e1_d115890e1_d115891e1\">A constant defined in a Script container of an object\n        is not available to other objects in the component.</p>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3615474\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3615474\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Script Container Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Juli 31, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Script Container Location for defining the ProcScript modules of the associated object. Description The Script code container can contain: Constant declarations with container scope System triggers Interactive triggers Operations Web triggers and operations (in DSP components) Functions Entries Note: Entities have two Script containers—Collection Script and Occurrence Script for defining entity-level (collection) and occurrence-level processing. A constant defined in a Script container of an object is not available to other objects in the component. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}